{"tid":1076561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"49歲九巴車長開工疑病發猝死","createTime":"2019-03-25T02:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T13:50:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1199594032fc00ace5e07e1ab76e4bae3ba0125c","tid":1076561,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190325/20640933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F20640933&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6Wo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=c96b2377\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F20640933&h=bdc8cb7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190325/20640933</a><br />\n<br />\n49歲九巴車長開工疑病發猝死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190325/large/a0905a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190325%2Flarge%2Fa0905a.gif&h=58d2994b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名九巴車長昨晨到巴士總站準備取車開工時暈倒，送院終告不治。警方不排除事主患有隱性疾病，突然病發致死。<br />\n<br />\n猝死的49歲車長雷振威（圖），在九巴工作超過22年，日常駕駛1A線巴士。據悉，死者是汽車交通運輸業總工會九巴分會九龍灣廠幹事會理事，工會發出通告表示對意外感到惋惜，又對死者家人致以深切慰問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同事做心外壓不果<br />\n<br />\n有同事形容事主脾氣很好，對他猝然而逝感到愕然及難過，但過往從未聽聞對方透露自己的身體狀況。<br />\n<br />\n昨清晨5時45分，雷在中秀茂坪巴士總站準備取車開工時，突然暈倒地上，另一車長見狀通知站長報警。現場消息指，有同事一度為雷做心外壓急救，救護員接報趕至將事主送院，惟經搶救後終告不治。九巴表示，涉事車長工作態度認真，熱誠和專業，受同事愛戴，公司對失去這位同事深表哀痛，已立即派員到醫院向其家人致以深切慰問。<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n五大保險公司推自願醫保產品<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n每年處理1,500宗精神病刑事案  法醫診斷殺人犯  「遲求助釀悲劇」"},{"pid":"609598cb96224b67c45f5e735fedbf48c487a0ef","tid":1076561,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c525499b662bff2f72fbb0886bee244ca4d392","tid":1076561,"uid":71425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"好mk"},{"pid":"710b561d5bf03155e62539ee6eaf3bbe1c507f90","tid":1076561,"uid":76793,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"不是男護士吸毒死<br />\n不是女教師跳樓死<br />\n<br />\n呢d死 係香港無咩人會討論<br />\n<br />\n點解？ 因為港豬中意食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fe6d449fa52af37942c67b1e05133059a461c0","tid":1076561,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"點解要登張咁嘅相..."},{"pid":"dba3ee5ddbb0a0641cb5bba6626f22eae0bcdc29","tid":1076561,"uid":95,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"巴士佬邊有人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b8148ca153f8adb98382163e899da31d7dc7d9","tid":1076561,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dba3ee5ddbb0a0641cb5bba6626f22eae0bcdc29","tid":1076561,"uid":95,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"巴士佬邊有人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"願他安息"},{"pid":"324a0aaada7b384cbde992e0a4641d7208040f60","tid":1076561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4de249e1d4b8dbab052f812834d5bf4534cbc3a6","tid":1076561,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"710b561d5bf03155e62539ee6eaf3bbe1c507f90","tid":1076561,"uid":76793,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"不是男護士吸毒死<br />\n不是女教師跳樓死<br />\n<br />\n呢d死 係香港無咩人會討論<br />\n<br />\n點解？ 因為港豬中意食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺香港只會理 政府俾人工 果班人（公